HEADWORD: Deteriorate
<hw>De*te"ri*o*rate</hw>
<pr>(d⟦esl⟧*t⟦emac⟧"r⟦icr⟧*⟦osl⟧*r⟦amac⟧t)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos>
<vmorph>[<pos>imp. & p. p.</pos> <conjf>Deteriorated</conjf>
