==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: deteriorate
<hw>de*te"ri*o*rate</hw>
<pr>(d⟦esl⟧*t⟦emac⟧"r⟦icr⟧*⟦osl⟧*r⟦amac⟧t)</pr>, <pos>v. i.</pos>
<def>To grow worse; to be impaired in quality; to degenerate.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Under such conditions, the mind rapidly
<qex>deteriorates</qex>.</q> <rj><qau>Goldsmith.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>deteriorating</ent>⟦br⟧
